original: Bärring, Sture Ferdinand, apotekare, Mörbylånga, f. 31/7/98 i Hälsingb. av tulluppsyn :man Magnus Alfred B. o. Botilda Ottolina Neuman. G. 26 m. Anna Ingeborg Lindström. Barn: Ulf Sture Magnus f. 27, Nils Ake Hjalmar 29, Bo Jörgen 31, Curt Göran 33. — Stud:ex. i Ystad 20, farm. kand. 24, apot:ex. 31. Elev v. Enhörningen i Gbg samt apot. i Jör-landa 20-23, anst. v. apot. i Eslöv, Älgen o. Lejonet i Sthlm, i Öregrund 31-33 (förest.), i Vetlanda 33-41 (förest. aderton mån.), v. Hjorten i Norrköp., priv. å apot. i Mörbylånga sed. 44.
translated: Bärring, Sture Ferdinand, pharmacist, Mörbylånga, b. 31/7/98 in Hälsingb. to customs inspector Magnus Alfred B. and Botilda Ottolina Neuman. Married on 26th with Anna Ingeborg Lindström. Children: Ulf Sture Magnus b. 27, Nils Ake Hjalmar b. 29, Bo Jörgen b. 31, Curt Göran b. 33. - Completed high school in Ystad in 1920, pharmaceutical degree in 1924, pharmacist degree in 1931. Was an apprentice at Enhörningen in Gbg and was employed at pharmacies in Jörlanda from 1920-23, Eslöv, Älgen, and Lejonet in Stockholm, Öregrund from 31-33 (Manager), Vetlanda 33-41 (Manager for eighteen months), Hjorten in Norrköping, own pharmacy in Mörbylånga since 44.
